definition: Chinese scholar tree (Sophora japonica)/Japanese pagoda tree

sentences.english: Effects of different urgings on germination rate of the Japonica seeds were studied in this paper.
sentences.chinese: 研究了不同處理方法對國槐種子發芽的影響。

sentences.english: Suggesting responses to the high CO2 concentration that Robinnia pseudoscacia and Sophorajaponica were the best apparent.
sentences.chinese: 其中刺槐和國槐對高CO2濃度的響應最爲顯著。
